(66, 7, 3, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', '작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/66.png', '2025-11-12 09:01:46', '2025-12-10 09:01:46'),
