(97, 10, 10, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다.', 'Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/97.png', '2025-09-21 12:18:35', '2025-10-11 12:18:35'),
