(297, 26, 14, '새로운 친구', 'CHAPTER', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. She held the letter close and read it one more time. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path.', NULL, '2026-04-14 22:35:58', '2026-04-27 22:35:58'),
(298, 26, 15, '돌아오는 길', 'CHAPTER', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/298.png', '2026-05-22 10:33:22', '2026-05-29 10:33:22'),
(299, 26, 16, '함께한 하루', 'CHAPTER', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/299.png', '2025-12-16 01:26:21', '2026-01-11 01:26:21'),
(300, 26, 17, '첫 만남', 'CHAPTER', '함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago.', NULL, '2026-04-10 07:58:14', '2026-05-01 07:58:14'),
(301, 27, 1, '숲으로', 'PAGE', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door.', NULL, '2026-02-22 04:37:36', '2026-03-12 04:37:36'),
(302, 27, 2, '작은 기적', 'PAGE', '작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/302.png', '2026-02-23 07:25:51', '2026-03-04 07:25:51'),
(303, 27, 3, '약속의 순간', 'PAGE', '비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다.', 'The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/303.png', '2025-03-17 08:38:40', '2025-04-02 08:38:40'),
(304, 27, 4, '작은 기적', 'PAGE', '작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/304.png', '2026-03-26 19:25:59', '2026-04-20 19:25:59'),
(305, 27, 5, '돌아오는 길', 'PAGE', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/305.png', '2026-06-15 03:59:15', '2026-06-19 03:59:15'),
(306, 27, 6, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. She held the letter close and read it one more time. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm.', NULL, '2026-02-02 03:57:57', '2026-02-07 03:57:57'),
(307, 27, 7, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다.', 'Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories.', NULL, '2025-06-28 05:26:09', '2025-07-04 05:26:09'),
(308, 27, 8, '함께한 하루', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. The train pulled away just as she reached the platform. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/308.png', '2025-05-27 09:32:10', '2025-05-28 09:32:10'),
(309, 27, 9, '첫 만남', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', NULL, '2026-01-22 13:34:37', '2026-01-28 13:34:37'),
