(395, 35, 11, '따뜻한 저녁', 'CHAPTER', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', NULL, '2025-04-14 16:48:58', '2025-04-29 16:48:58'),
