(611, 54, 12, '비 오는 날', 'CHAPTER', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다.', 'She held the letter close and read it one more time. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate.', NULL, '2026-04-18 06:18:00', '2026-04-27 06:18:00'),
(612, 54, 13, '따뜻한 저녁', 'CHAPTER', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. She held the letter close and read it one more time.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/612.png', '2025-06-10 07:01:16', '2025-06-19 07:01:16'),
(613, 54, 14, '따뜻한 저녁', 'CHAPTER', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path.', NULL, '2025-12-05 04:54:55', '2026-01-04 04:54:55'),
(614, 54, 15, '돌아오는 길', 'CHAPTER', '달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'Nobody in town could explain where the music came from.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/614.png', '2026-04-24 07:41:50', '2026-05-21 07:41:50'),
(615, 54, 16, '마지막 인사', 'CHAPTER', '아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The mountain path was steep, but the view was worth it. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/615.png', '2025-05-25 02:31:42', '2025-05-26 02:31:42'),
(616, 55, 1, '따뜻한 저녁', 'POEM', '작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다.', 'Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/616.png', '2026-05-27 19:42:42', '2026-06-08 19:42:42'),
(617, 55, 2, '새로운 친구', 'POEM', '함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다.', 'Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. She held the letter close and read it one more time. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/617.png', '2025-04-25 12:08:17', '2025-05-04 12:08:17'),
(618, 55, 3, '비 오는 날', 'POEM', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. She held the letter close and read it one more time. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/618.png', '2025-11-12 11:07:04', '2025-11-18 11:07:04'),
(619, 55, 4, '돌아오는 길', 'POEM', '숲속에서 들려오는 소리에 귀를 기울였습니다. 달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'She held the letter close and read it one more time. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. Nobody expected the small boat to survive the storm. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/619.png', '2026-03-23 11:56:00', '2026-03-27 11:56:00'),
(620, 55, 5, '따뜻한 저녁', 'POEM', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. She held the letter close and read it one more time.', NULL, '2025-08-08 21:02:40', '2025-08-27 21:02:40'),
(621, 55, 6, '함께한 하루', 'POEM', '겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/621.png', '2025-07-19 07:45:42', '2025-07-22 07:45:42'),
(622, 55, 7, '돌아오는 길', 'POEM', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/622.png', '2026-05-05 00:21:35', '2026-06-01 00:21:35'),
(623, 55, 8, '따뜻한 저녁', 'POEM', '바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/623.png', '2026-04-20 16:35:05', '2026-05-04 16:35:05'),
