(644, 57, 2, '마지막 인사', 'CHAPTER', '모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. Every winter, the lake froze just enough to walk across. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/644.png', '2025-03-04 20:33:08', '2025-03-31 20:33:08'),
