(835, 71, 10, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. She held the letter close and read it one more time. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves.', NULL, '2025-09-01 20:17:55', '2025-10-01 20:17:55'),
(836, 71, 11, '작은 결심', 'PAGE', '함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다.', 'The little village woke up slowly under the morning light. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. A warm cup of tea waited for him on the table. The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/836.png', '2025-04-21 13:46:24', '2025-04-27 13:46:24'),
(837, 71, 12, '마지막 인사', 'PAGE', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. She held the letter close and read it one more time. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/837.png', '2025-05-09 09:29:29', '2025-05-12 09:29:29'),
(838, 71, 13, '다시 만난 날', 'PAGE', '구름 사이로 햇살이 비치자 모두가 미소지었습니다.', 'Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago. Every evening, the baker left a loaf of bread by the door. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/838.png', '2026-02-20 22:04:52', '2026-03-09 22:04:52'),
(839, 71, 14, '돌아오는 길', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 바람이 불 때마다 나뭇잎이 춤을 추듯 흔들렸습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', NULL, '2025-12-23 18:06:30', '2026-01-08 18:06:30'),
(840, 71, 15, '돌아오는 길', 'PAGE', '아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다.', 'The child looked out the window and smiled at the falling snow. The fox watched them from behind a fallen tree. The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/840.png', '2025-04-24 01:10:24', '2025-04-27 01:10:24'),
(841, 71, 16, '약속의 순간', 'PAGE', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/841.png', '2025-06-18 23:46:57', '2025-06-20 23:46:57'),
(842, 71, 17, '작은 기적', 'PAGE', '겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 달빛 아래에서 두 친구는 오래도록 이야기를 나누었습니다. 작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다.', 'The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/842.png', '2025-12-18 04:31:07', '2025-12-27 04:31:07'),
(843, 72, 1, '새로운 친구', 'PAGE', '작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. The dog barked twice, then ran ahead down the path. A soft breeze carried the smell of fresh bread through the street.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/843.png', '2025-09-27 02:40:11', '2025-10-11 02:40:11'),
(844, 72, 2, '비 오는 날', 'PAGE', '오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 새로운 친구를 만난 순간, 마음이 두근거렸습니다.', 'She found an old key hidden inside the wooden box. Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', NULL, '2025-05-31 08:26:28', '2025-06-16 08:26:28'),
(845, 72, 3, '숲으로', 'PAGE', '함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다. 처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다. 작은 실수도 함께 웃으며 넘길 수 있었습니다.', 'The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. Rain tapped gently on the roof while they slept. The last page of the book was missing, and no one knew why.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/845.png', '2025-03-12 13:51:58', '2025-03-13 13:51:58'),
(846, 72, 4, '새로운 친구', 'PAGE', '오랜 기다림 끝에 반가운 소식이 도착했습니다. 비가 그치자 무지개가 마을을 감쌌습니다. 작은 마을에 사는 아이는 매일 창밖을 바라보았습니다. 모두가 잠든 밤, 별들이 조용히 이야기를 나누었습니다.', 'The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate. She held the letter close and read it one more time.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/846.png', '2025-10-28 23:27:01', '2025-11-24 23:27:01'),
