(1158, 96, 5, '약속의 순간', 'POEM', '작은 발걸음이 모여 커다란 여행이 되었습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'The stars seemed closer than ever that quiet night. She held the letter close and read it one more time. A single candle lit the whole room with a warm glow. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. He took a deep breath and stepped through the old gate.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/1158.png', '2025-03-13 00:02:45', '2025-04-08 00:02:45'),
