(1194, 99, 2, '돌아오는 길', 'CHAPTER', '아이는 손을 흔들며 친구에게 인사했습니다.', 'The garden was full of flowers no one remembered planting. The old clock in the hallway had stopped ticking years ago.', 'https://cdn.sangsangseoga.com/page/1194.png', '2025-10-25 14:54:08', '2025-10-31 14:54:08'),
