(1411, 118, 18, '작은 기적', 'CHAPTER', '처음엔 무서웠지만 곧 용기를 내기로 했습니다. 함께라면 무엇이든 해낼 수 있을 것 같았습니다. 겨울이 지나고 봄이 오자 나무에 새싹이 돋았습니다.', 'Deep in the forest, something rustled quietly among the leaves. Two old friends sat by the river and shared their stories. Nobody in town could explain where the music came from. The children built a small boat out of paper and leaves. The lantern flickered as the wind grew stronger outside.', NULL, '2026-05-27 12:34:25', '2026-06-01 12:34:25'),
